[I] Additional service providers for KAccounts framework

[T] KAccounts-Providers is a KDE framework that provides additional support for
[T] online accounts integration in KDE applications. It works in conjunction
[T] with KAccounts (The KDE Account Manager) to allow users to easily set up
[T] their online accounts and make these accesible to other KDE software.

[U] https://www.kde.org

